hotos-and-texts-in-blackmail-plot&quot;>;如 &lt;em>;Semafor&lt;/em>; 周四&lt;/a>;首次报道。&lt; /p>; &lt;p id=&quot;0aJnUH&quot;>;该情节发生在阿伦和女子萨科亚·布莱克伍德之间几周的短信中。布莱克伍德冒充了多个虚假身份，包括阿隆的前恋人身份，以向首席执行官索要露骨的照片，然后威胁要公开这些照片 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.cnbc.com/2023/07/20/ ceo-catfish-new-york-woman-sentenced-in-extortion-bid.html&quot;>;除非她收到 30 万美元&lt;/a>;。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;v8z10W&quot;>;该案件于去年 7 月首次报道，但掩盖了阿伦的身份，仅称他为一家上市公司的首席执行官。 Aron 在 X（以前称为 Twitter）上发帖证实自己是该阴谋的受害者...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/12/ 23914298/amc-ceo-blackmail-extortion-plot-memestock-adam-aron&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/12/23914298/amc-ceo-blackmail-extortion-plot-memestock-adam-aron" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/12/23914298/amc-ceo-blackmail-extortion-plot-memestock-adam-aron</id><author><name>马克纳·凯利</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-10-12T11:00:11-04:00</published><updated> 2023-10-12T11:00:11-04:00</updated><title>荣耀宣布今年第三款可折叠手机</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Honor Magic VS2 蓝色、粉色、展开。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/JM1C3ZSQJ_RiGnRuUTt05NH8-KE=/0x0:1350x900/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72748158/Screen_Shot_2023_10_12_at_2.51.2 4_PM.0 .jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Magic VS2 显示折叠和展开。&lt;/em>; |图片：荣誉&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;sNo6Fr&quot;>;&lt;a href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F% 2Fwww.hihonor.com%2Fcn%2Fphones%2Fhonor-magic-vs-2%2F&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2023%2F10%2F12%2F23913011%2Fhonor- magic-vs2-price-release-date-specs-features-china-launch&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;荣耀 Magic VS2&lt;/a>; 是前华为子品牌在中国推出的第三款新可折叠手机继&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23791047/honor-magic-v2-foldable-china-launch-release-date-price-specs-details-hinge&quot;>;推出后四个月7 月份的 Magic V2&lt;/a>; 和&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.gsmarena.com/honor_v_purse_launches_in_china_a_thin_and_light_outward_foldable_with_a_unique_style-news-59956.php&quot;>;上个月的 Magic V 钱包&lt;/a>;。这还不包括今年早些时候 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23743664/honor-magic-vs-review-foldable-phone&quot;>;Magic VS&lt;/a>; 的国际发布。 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2022/11/23/23474820/honors-magic-vs-price-release-date-features-foldable-smartphone&quot;>;2022 年在中国发布&lt;/a>; 。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;jQx6pm&quot;>;毫不奇怪，考虑到两次发布之间的间隔，Magic VS2 与荣耀之前的设备相比并不是一次彻底的改进。它的重量略轻，为 229 克，而 Magic V2 最轻版本的重量为 231 克，但折叠后厚度为 10.7 毫米，略厚。 （Magic V2 的厚度在 9.9 至 10.1 毫米之间。）有趣的是，它还运行上一代高通 Snapdragon 8 Plus Gen 1 处理器，而 V2 则采用...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot; https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/12/23913011/honor-magic-vs2-price-release-date-specs-features-china-launch&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/12/23913011/honor-magic-vs2-price-release-date-specs-features-china-launch" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/12/23913011/honor-magic-vs2-price-release-date-specs-features-china-launch</id><author><name>乔恩·波特</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-10-12T10:54:08-04:00</published><updated> 2023-10-12T10:54:08-04:00</updated><title>上一轮合同谈判破裂后，SAG-AFTRA 罢工仍在继续</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;SAG-AFTRA 徽标位于“SAG-AFTRA ON STRIKE!”上方1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72748104/c68f5e_432958c67d674916923da56d41a2b000_mv2.0.jpeg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：SAG-AFTRA&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;Gg&quot; wNeE&quot;>;在&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/9/26/23889334/wga-strike-end-hollywood-writers&quot;>;美国作家协会最终获胜&lt;/a>;之后&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/10/23911279/wga-contract-ratification-vote&quot;>;批准新的劳动合同&lt;/a>;与 &lt;a href=&quot;https:// /w